text: Volnoye () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Volnenskoye Rural Settlement of Koshekhablsky District, Adygea, Russia. The population of this village was 3595 as of 2018.Численность постоянного населения по МО и населенным пунктам Республики Адыгея по состоянию на 1 января 2018 года There are 37 streets. == Geography == The village is located on the left bank of the Laba River, 36 km south from Koshekhabl. == References == Category:Rural localities in Koshekhablsky District
title: Volnoye, Republic of Adygea
